00:30:03,970 --> 00:30:06,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">主人的战争需要那东西
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The master wants it for the war.</font>

284
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:11,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们认为我们有魔戒
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They think we have the Ring.</font>

285
00:30:11,940 --> 00:30:14,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们一旦发现我们没有  我们就死定了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">As soon as they find out we don't, we're dead.</font>

286
00:30:16,240 --> 00:30:18,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就只咬一口
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Just a mouthful...</font>

287
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:19,570
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">来一块腰窝肉
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...a bit of the flank.</font>

288
00:30:26,370 --> 00:30:29,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">看起来我们的菜谱上又有肉吃了 小伙子们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Looks like meat's back on the menu, boys.</font>

289
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:37,800
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">皮聘
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Pippin.</font>

290
00:30:38,010 --> 00:30:39,680
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们快逃
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let's go.</font>

291
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:49,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">想跑
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Go on.</font>

292
00:30:49,850 --> 00:30:51,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">去找援助
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Call for help.</font>

293
00:30:52,690 --> 00:30:53,820
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">尖叫呀!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Squeal.</font>

294
00:30:54,020 --> 00:30:57,150
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">看现在还有什么能救你
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">No one's going to save you now.</font>

295
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:07,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">皮聘!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Pippin!</font>

296
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:34,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">血红的太阳升起来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A red sun rises.</font>

297
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:37,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">昨晚一定曾经发生杀戮
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Blood has been spilled this night.</font>

298
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:11,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">洛汗国的骑士
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Riders of Rohan...</font>

299
00:32:11,430 --> 00:32:13,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">骠骑国有什么消息?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...what news from the Mark?</font>

300
00:32:41,630 --> 00:32:46,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一个精灵 一个凡人和一个矮人闯进骠骑国有何贵干?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What business does an Elf, a Man and a Dwarf have in the Riddermark?</font>

301
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:48,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快说!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Speak quickly!</font>

302
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:53,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">骑士 你先报上名来 我就说出我的名字
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Give me your name, horse-master, and I shall give you mine.</font>

303
00:33:02,280 --> 00:33:04,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我一剑砍断你的人头  矮子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I would cut off your head, Dwarf...</font>

304
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:07,620
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">要不是你长的那么矮
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...if it stood but a little higher from the ground.</font>

305
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:10,700
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你会先一箭毙命
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You would die before your stroke fell.</font>

306
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:21,300
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我是亚拉冈 亚拉松之子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am Aragorn, son of Arathorn.</font>

307
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:25,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是金雳 葛罗音之子  勒苟拉斯 来自幽暗森林
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This is Gimli, son of Gloin, and Legolas of the Woodland Realm.</font>

308
00:33:26,010 --> 00:33:29,260
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们是骠骑王希优顿的朋友
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We are friends of Rohan and of Theoden, your king.</font>

309
00:33:31,010 --> 00:33:34,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优顿已经分不出敌友
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Theoden no longer recognizes friend from foe.</font>

310
00:33:35,020 --> 00:33:37,190
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他连自家人都认不得
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Not even his own kin.</font>

311
00:33:41,690 --> 00:33:43,690
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨尔曼在国王身上下毒
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Saruman has poisoned the mind of the king...</font>

312
00:33:43,860 --> 00:33:45,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">将这片土地占为己有
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...and claimed lordship over these lands.</font>

313
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:50,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的伙伴们都誓死效忠洛汗国
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My company are those loyal to Rohan.</font>

314
00:33:50,910 --> 00:33:52,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">所以才会被放逐
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And for that, we are banished.</font>

315
00:33:54,750 --> 00:33:58,040
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">白袍巫师诡计多端
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The White Wizard is cunning.</font>

316
00:33:58,710 --> 00:34:01,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">听说他到处神出鬼没
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He walks here and there, they say...</font>

317
00:34:01,340 --> 00:34:03,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">是个身披白色斗蓬的老头
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...as an old man hooded and cloaked.</font>

318
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:08,970
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他的爪牙也逃过我们的监视
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And everywhere, his spies slip past our nets.</font>

319
00:34:09,140 --> 00:34:11,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们不是他派来的间谍
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We are no spies.</font>

320
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:14,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们在追赶一群跑向草原西面的强兽人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We track a party of Uruk-hai westward across the plain.</font>

321
00:34:14,770 --> 00:34:17,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们抓走我们两个朋友
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They have taken two of our friends captive.</font>

322
00:34:17,890 --> 00:34:20,400
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们昨晚歼灭了那伙强兽人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The Uruks are destroyed. We slaughtered them during the night.</font>

323
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:23,690
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是其中有两个哈比人  你没看见两个哈比人和他们一起吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But there were two Hobbits. Did you see two Hobbits with them?</font>

324
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:26,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们身材矮小 在你们眼里像小孩一样
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They would be small. Only children to your eyes.</font>

325
00:34:30,200 --> 00:34:32,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们没留下活口
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We left none alive.</font>

326
00:34:32,830 --> 00:34:35,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们把尸体堆起来烧掉
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We piled the carcasses and burned them.</font>

327
00:34:41,250 --> 00:34:42,500
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们死了?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Dead?</font>

328
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:47,220
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">很遗憾
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am sorry.</font>

329
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:55,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">哈苏风 阿罗德
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Hasufel! Arod!</font>

330
00:34:56,890 --> 00:35:01,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希望这两匹马能带给你们好运
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">May these horses bear you to better fortune than their former masters.</font>

331
00:35:02,770 --> 00:35:04,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">后会有期
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Farewell.</font>

332
00:35:09,570 --> 00:35:11,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">去找你们的朋友
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Look for your friends.</font>

333
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:14,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但别心存希望
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But do not trust to hope.</font>

334
00:35:16,200 --> 00:35:18,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们早已失去希望
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It has forsaken these lands.</font>

335
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们往北走!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We ride north!</font>

336
00:36:11,550 --> 00:36:13,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是他们的小腰带
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's one of their wee belts.</font>

337
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:29,230
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们对不起他们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We failed them.</font>

338
00:36:43,290 --> 00:36:45,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一个哈比人躺在这儿
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A Hobbit lay here.</font>

339
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:49,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">另一个在这儿
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And the other.</font>

340
00:36:59,810 --> 00:37:01,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们在地上爬行
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They crawled.</font>

341
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:07,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">而双手被绑住
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Their hands were bound.</font>

342
00:37:19,740 --> 00:37:21,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但他们割断绳索
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Their bonds were cut.</font>

343
00:37:37,090 --> 00:37:39,220
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">然后跑到这里
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They ran over here.</font>

344
00:37:42,850 --> 00:37:44,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">有人在追他们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They were followed.</font>

345
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:48,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的腰带!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The belt!</font>

346
00:37:52,900 --> 00:37:54,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快跑!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Run!</font>

347
00:37:57,780 --> 00:37:59,070
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们的足迹逐渐远离战场
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Tracks lead away from the battle...</font>

348
00:38:03,910 --> 00:38:06,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">逃进法贡森林
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...into Fangorn Forest.</font>

349
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:08,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">法贡森林?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Fangorn?</font>

350
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:11,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们疯了么?居然跑进那里
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What madness drove them in there?</font>

351
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:31,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">甩掉他们了吗? 好像甩掉了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Did we lose him? I think we lost him.</font>

352
00:38:38,610 --> 00:38:42,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我要把你们的心脏给挖出来!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'm going to rip out your filthy little innards!</font>

353
00:38:48,290 --> 00:38:49,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">过来这里!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Come here!</font>

354
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:57,340
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">树!爬到树上去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Trees. Climb a tree.</font>

355
00:39:06,680 --> 00:39:08,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他已经走了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He's gone.</font>

356
00:39:20,490 --> 00:39:22,820
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">梅里!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Merry!</font>

357
00:39:34,290 --> 00:39:38,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我要在你的肚子上戳一个洞!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let's put a maggot hole in your belly!</font>

358
00:39:45,810 --> 00:39:47,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快跑呀 梅里!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Run, Merry!</font>

359
00:39:57,150 --> 00:40:01,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">是小半兽人?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Little Orcs.</font>

360
00:40:01,650 --> 00:40:03,990
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他在说话 梅里  这棵树在说话
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's talking, Merry. The tree is talking.</font>

361
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:06,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">树?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Tree?</font>

362
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:09,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我不是树
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am no tree!</font>

363
00:40:09,450 --> 00:40:11,620
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我是树人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am an Ent.</font>

364
00:40:12,210 --> 00:40:14,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">守树者
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A tree-herder.</font>

365
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">森林的守护者
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A shepherd of the forest.</font>

366
00:40:17,050 --> 00:40:18,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">别跟他说话  梅里
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Don't talk to it, Merry.</font>

367
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:20,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">别刺激他说话!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Don't encourage it!</font>

368
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:24,800
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">有些人叫我树包
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Treebeard, some call me.</font>

369
00:40:24,970 --> 00:40:26,930
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你站在哪一边?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And whose side are you on?</font>

370
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:29,180
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">哪一边?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Side?</font>

371
00:40:29,390 --> 00:40:32,230
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我不站在哪一边
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am on nobody's side...</font>

372
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:37,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">因为没有人站在我这一边  小半兽人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...because nobody's on my side, little Orc.</font>

373
00:40:38,780 --> 00:40:43,400
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">没有人关心这片森林了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Nobody cares for the woods anymore.</font>

374
00:40:43,780 --> 00:40:46,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们不是半兽人 是哈比人!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We're not Orcs! We're Hobbits!</font>

375
00:40:46,370 --> 00:40:48,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">哈比人?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Hobbits?</font>

376
00:40:49,910 --> 00:40:54,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我没听过哈比人这玩意
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Never heard of a Hobbit before.</font>

377
00:40:55,960 --> 00:41:00,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">听起来像是半兽人的幌子!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Sounds like Orc mischief to me!</font>

378
