694
01:10:19,270 --> 01:10:21,400
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">给我  梅里!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Give me it back. Merry!</font>

695
01:10:23,280 --> 01:10:24,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">发生什么事了?!
