696
01:10:25,490 --> 01:10:26,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它抓住我的腿了!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's got my leg!</font>

697
01:10:27,280 --> 01:10:28,780
