</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Merry!</font>

698
01:10:48,180 --> 01:10:49,760
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">救命!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Help!</font>

