701
01:11:00,900 --> 01:11:05,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">吃土  挖深点  喝点水
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Eat earth. Dig deep. Drink water.</font>

702
01:11:06,360 --> 01:11:08,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">去睡觉
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Go to sleep.</font>

703
01:11:09,280 --> 01:11:11,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">跟你一起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Away with you.</font>

704
01:11:11,330 --> 01:11:14,620
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快点  森林就要醒了
