01:11:15,160 --> 01:11:17,120
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它很危险
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It isn't safe.</font>

706
01:11:19,790 --> 01:11:23,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这些树疯了  很危险
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The trees have grown wild and dangerous.</font>

707
01:11:23,880 --> 01:11:26,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">愤怒吞噬了他们的心
