708
01:11:27,760 --> 01:11:29,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们的思想邪恶
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Black are their thoughts.</font>

709
01:11:29,550 --> 01:11:32,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">仇恨强烈
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Strong is their hate.</font>

710
01:11:32,260 --> 01:11:35,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">如果他们能伤害你们  他们就会这么干
