01:12:06,710 --> 01:12:09,930
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们把她们弄丢了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We lost them.</font>

720
01:12:10,090 --> 01:12:15,180
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">到现在还找不到她们
