</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...when all your life seems to shrink.</font>

747
01:14:43,900 --> 01:14:48,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你受到四面高墙禁锢
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The walls of your bower closing in about you.</font>

748
01:14:48,280 --> 01:14:52,870
