01:18:16,740 --> 01:18:18,280
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他是恶兆的信差
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He's a herald of woe.</font>

760
01:18:18,450 --> 01:18:22,910
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你近来似乎不太欢迎来访者
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The courtesy of your hall is somewhat lessened of late...</font>

761
01:18:23,990 --> 01:18:25,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优顿王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...Theoden King.</font>

762
01:18:26,120 --> 01:18:28,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他是不受欢迎的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He's not welcome.</font>

763
01:18:29,620 --> 01:18:34,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我为什么要欢迎你?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Why should I welcome you...</font>

764
01:18:35,460 --> 01:18:39,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">乌鸦嘴甘道夫?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...Gandalf Stormcrow?</font>

765
01:18:39,300 --> 01:18:42,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">说得好 王上
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A just question, my liege.</font>

766
01:18:42,760 --> 01:18:49,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这名江湖术士这么晚才跑来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Late is the hour in which this conjurer chooses to appear.</font>

767
01:18:50,560 --> 01:18:52,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我替他取名为噩耗
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Lathspell I name him.</font>

768
01:18:52,810 --> 01:18:55,690
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">噩耗就是不受欢迎的恶客
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Ill news is an ill guest.</font>

769
01:18:55,860 --> 01:19:00,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">给我闭嘴  别在这儿搬弄是非
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Be silent. Keep your forked tongue behind your teeth.</font>

770
01:19:00,610 --> 01:19:02,530
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我通过烈火和死亡的试炼
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I have not passed through fire and death...</font>

771
01:19:02,660 --> 01:19:05,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不是为了跟蠢材做口舌之争
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...to bandy crooked words with a witless worm.</font>

772
01:19:06,870 --> 01:19:08,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他的手杖
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">His staff.</font>

773
01:19:09,160 --> 01:19:13,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我叫你们没收巫师的手杖
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I told you to take the wizard's staff.</font>

774
01:19:16,670 --> 01:19:18,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优顿
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Theoden...</font>

775
01:19:19,170 --> 01:19:21,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">塞哲尔之子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...son of Thengel...</font>

776
01:19:23,510 --> 01:19:25,850
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你活在阴影下太久了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...too long have you sat in the Shadows.</font>

777
01:19:28,850 --> 01:19:32,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你最好乖乖别动
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I would stay still if I were you.</font>

778
01:19:32,270 --> 01:19:34,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">听我说
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Hearken to me!</font>

779
01:19:39,860 --> 01:19:44,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我把你从咒语中释放出来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I release you from the spell.</font>

780
01:19:55,710 --> 01:19:58,760
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你在这里没有力量
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You have no power here...</font>

781
01:19:58,920 --> 01:20:02,550
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">灰袍甘道夫
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...Gandalf the Grey.</font>

782
01:20:07,970 --> 01:20:13,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼 我要把你逼出来  就像把剧毒逼出伤口
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I will draw you, Saruman, as poison is drawn from a wound.</font>

783
01:20:22,490 --> 01:20:24,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">等等
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Wait.</font>

784
01:20:25,450 --> 01:20:29,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我一走 希优顿就会死
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">If I go, Theoden dies.</font>

785
01:20:30,000 --> 01:20:32,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你杀不了我
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You did not kill me...</font>

786
01:20:32,370 --> 01:20:34,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">更杀不了他
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...you will not kill him.</font>

787
01:20:38,460 --> 01:20:40,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">洛汗国是我的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Rohan is mine.</font>

788
01:20:41,630 --> 01:20:42,970
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">出来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Be gone.</font>

789
01:21:27,470 --> 01:21:29,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你很面熟
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I know your face.</font>

790
01:21:34,180 --> 01:21:35,440
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">伊欧玟
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Eowyn.</font>

791
01:21:37,770 --> 01:21:39,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">伊欧玟
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Eowyn.</font>

792
01:21:47,320 --> 01:21:48,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">甘道夫
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Gandalf?</font>

793
01:21:49,030 --> 01:21:51,910
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你又重获自由了 我的朋友
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Breathe the free air again, my friend.</font>

794
01:22:05,260 --> 01:22:07,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的梦里充满了黑暗
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Dark have been my dreams of late.</font>

795
01:22:12,010 --> 01:22:15,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你从前的力量会恢复的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Your fingers would remember their old strength better...</font>

796
01:22:15,930 --> 01:22:18,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">只要你握住宝剑
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...if they grasped your sword.</font>

797
01:23:04,020 --> 01:23:05,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我只想
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I've only...</font>

798
01:23:06,190 --> 01:23:09,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">自始至终只想服侍您  王上
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...ever served you, my lord.</font>

799
01:23:09,400 --> 01:23:14,410
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你只想用邪术让我臣服于你
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Your leechcraft would have had me crawling on all fours like a beast!</font>

800
01:23:15,410 --> 01:23:17,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">请放逐我吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Send me not from your sight.</font>

801
01:23:19,670 --> 01:23:22,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不 王上 饶了他吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">No, my lord! No, my lord.</font>

802
01:23:22,580 --> 01:23:23,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让他走
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let him go.</font>

803
01:23:24,500 --> 01:23:27,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">已经流了太多血了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Enough blood has been spilt on his account.</font>

804
01:23:36,890 --> 01:23:39,230
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">给我滚开!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Get out of my way!</font>

805
01:23:41,440 --> 01:23:44,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优顿王万岁!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Hail, Theoden King!</font>

806
01:24:09,210 --> 01:24:11,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优德呢?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is Theodred?</font>

807
01:24:14,760 --> 01:24:17,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我儿子呢?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is my son?</font>

808
01:25:44,520 --> 01:25:46,230
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">永志花
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Simbelmyn?</font>

809
01:25:51,400 --> 01:25:55,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它一直生长在先王的坟上
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Ever has it grown on the tombs of my forebearers.</font>

810
01:25:58,870 --> 01:26:01,830
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">现在也将永远覆盖在吾儿之墓
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Now it shall cover the grave of my son.</font>

811
01:26:03,910 --> 01:26:07,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">厄运应该降临在我身上
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Alas that these evil days should be mine.</font>

812
01:26:08,540 --> 01:26:12,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">少年英年早逝 老人苟延残喘
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The young perish and the old linger.</font>

813
01:26:13,550 --> 01:26:15,630
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但我还是该活着
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That I should live...</font>

814
01:26:15,800 --> 01:26:19,180
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">看着我的王国灭亡
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...to see the last days of my house.</font>

815
01:26:20,430 --> 01:26:24,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优德的死不是你的错
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Theodred's death was not of your making.</font>

816
01:26:27,350 --> 01:26:30,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">白发人不该送黑发人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">No parent should have to bury their child.</font>

817
01:26:47,460 --> 01:26:49,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他生前很坚强
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He was strong in life.</font>

818
01:26:50,460 --> 01:26:54,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">死后也将与你的先王同在
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">His spirit will find its way to the halls of your fathers.</font>

819
01:27:38,630 --> 01:27:40,510
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们措手不及
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They had no warning.</font>

820
01:27:40,680 --> 01:27:43,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">手无寸铁
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They were unarmed.</font>

821
01:27:43,550 --> 01:27:47,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">现在野人正穿越西谷  烧毁经过的一切
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Now the Wild Men are moving through the Westfold, burning as they go.</font>

822
01:27:48,520 --> 01:27:50,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">干草  茅屋和树木
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Rick, cot and tree.</font>

823
01:27:50,810 --> 01:27:53,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">妈妈呢?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is Mama?</font>

824
01:27:53,810 --> 01:27:58,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这只是萨鲁曼大军的一小部份
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This is but a taste of the terror that Saruman will unleash.</font>

825
01:27:58,240 --> 01:28:02,570
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他和索伦结盟后势力更强大
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">All the more potent for he is driven now by fear of Sauron.</font>

826
01:28:04,200 --> 01:28:07,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你必须正面迎敌
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Ride out and meet him head on.</font>

827
01:28:07,910 --> 01:28:11,420
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">引开他的大军 保护老弱妇孺
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Draw him away from your women and children.</font>

828
01:28:11,750 --> 01:28:13,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你一定要迎战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You must fight.</font>

829
01:28:13,540 --> 01:28:17,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">目前有两千名精兵向北而来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You have 2000 good men riding north as we speak.</font>

830
01:28:17,550 --> 01:28:19,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">伊欧墨对你忠心耿耿
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Eomer is loyal to you.</font>

831
01:28:19,380 --> 01:28:22,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他的部下会回来为他们的国王奋战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">His men will return and fight for their king.</font>

832
01:28:22,220 --> 01:28:26,140
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们离这儿有三百里路
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They will be 300 leagues from here by now.</font>

833
01:28:29,810 --> 01:28:32,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">伊欧墨救不了我们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Eomer cannot help us.</font>

834
01:28:32,690 --> 01:28:34,440
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我知道你要我怎么做
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I know what it is you want of me...</font>

835
01:28:34,650 --> 01:28:37,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是我不能让我的人民白白去送死
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...but I will not bring further death to my people.</font>

836
01:28:39,570 --> 01:28:41,280
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我不想冒险全面开战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I will not risk open war.</font>

837
01:28:43,490 --> 01:28:46,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">敌人已向你宣战  不管你想不想冒险
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Open war is upon you, whether you would risk it or not.</font>

838
01:28:51,120 --> 01:28:52,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就我所知
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">When last I looked...</font>

839
01:28:53,210 --> 01:28:56,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我希优顿才是洛汗国国王  不是亚拉冈
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...Theoden, not Aragorn, was king of Rohan.</font>

840
01:29:03,630 --> 01:29:05,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">国王的命令是什么
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Then what is the king's decision?</font>

841
01:29:11,520 --> 01:29:12,850
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">国王下令
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">By order of the king...</font>

842
01:29:13,020 --> 01:29:14,480
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">全城军民撤退
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...the city must empty.</font>

843
01:29:15,650 --> 01:29:18,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">撤退到圣盔谷碉堡
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We make for the refuge of Helm's Deep.</font>

844
01:29:18,820 --> 01:29:22,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不要携带笨重的财宝只带必需品
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Do not burden yourself with treasures. Take only what provisions you need.</font>

845
01:29:22,940 --> 01:29:24,400
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">圣盔谷
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Helm's Deep.</font>

846
01:29:24,610 --> 01:29:28,120
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他应该一决死战 而不是逃之夭夭
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They flee to the mountains when they should stand and fight.</font>

847
01:29:28,280 --> 01:29:30,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一国之君就应该捍卫人民
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Who will defend them if not their king?</font>

848
01:29:30,450 --> 01:29:32,910
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他这么做也是为了人民着想
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He's only doing what he thinks is best for his people.</font>

849
01:29:33,080 --> 01:29:34,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">圣盔谷以前救过他们一命
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Helm's Deep has saved them in the past.</font>

850
01:29:35,040 --> 01:29:38,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那道峡谷无路可退  希优顿这是自寻死路
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There is no way out of that ravine. Theoden is walking into a trap.</font>

851
01:29:39,130 --> 01:29:41,300
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他认为他们在那儿很安全
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He thinks he's leading them to safety.</font>

852
01:29:41,510 --> 01:29:43,630
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是他们会惨遭屠杀
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What they will get is a massacre.</font>

