<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这当然是无稽之谈
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...which is, of course, ridiculous.</font>

1044
01:47:17,030 --> 01:47:19,280
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我没事 别紧张
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's all right. Nobody panic.</font>

1045
01:47:19,740 --> 01:47:21,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我是故意凸槌的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That was deliberate. It was deliberate.</font>

1046
01:47:23,700 --> 01:47:27,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我很久没见我侄女笑过了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I haven't seen my niece smile for a long time.</font>

1047
01:47:27,790 --> 01:47:30,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">她父亲的尸体被带回来的时候  她还是个孩子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">She was a girl when they brought her father back dead.</font>

1048
01:47:30,710 --> 01:47:33,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">被兽人杀了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Cut down by Orcs.</font>

1049
01:47:33,170 --> 01:47:36,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">她看着她母亲悲痛欲绝
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">She watched her mother succumb to grief.</font>

1050
01:47:36,800 --> 01:47:41,420
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">只留下她孤单一人活在恐惧中还要照顾她的国王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Then she was left alone, to tend her king in growing fear.</font>

1051
01:47:41,590 --> 01:47:46,140
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">命中注定要等待一个会像父亲一样疼爱她的人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Doomed to wait upon an old man who should have loved her as a father.</font>

1052
01:47:56,150 --> 01:47:58,530
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">金雳
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Gimli.</font>

1053
01:47:58,690 --> 01:48:00,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不  我不能
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">No, I couldn't</font>

1054
01:48:00,940 --> 01:48:02,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我真的不能
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I really couldn't.</font>

1055
01:48:07,280 --> 01:48:08,910
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我做了些炖肉
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I made some stew.</font>

1056
01:48:09,080 --> 01:48:12,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不是很多  不过是热的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It isn't much, but it's hot.</font>

1057
01:48:20,170 --> 01:48:22,220
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">谢谢
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

1058
01:48:42,740 --> 01:48:45,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 很好吃     - 真的?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- It's good.     - Really?</font>

1059
01:48:49,200 --> 01:48:52,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">叔叔告诉了我一些奇怪的事情
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My uncle told me a strange thing.</font>

1060
01:48:53,910 --> 01:48:57,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他说你和我祖父塞哲尔一起战斗
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He said that you rode to war with Thengel, my grandfather.</font>

1061
01:48:58,380 --> 01:49:00,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但我认为他错了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But he must be mistaken.</font>

1062
01:49:01,130 --> 01:49:05,550
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优顿王的记忆很好  那时候他还是个孩子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">King Theoden has a good memory. He was only a small child at the time.</font>

1063
01:49:06,680 --> 01:49:09,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">而你至少有60岁
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Then you must be at least 60.</font>

1064
01:49:11,970 --> 01:49:13,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">70?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Seventy?</font>

1065
01:49:13,980 --> 01:49:15,640
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不会是80!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But you cannot be 80!</font>

1066
01:49:18,980 --> 01:49:20,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">87
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Eighty-seven.</font>

1067
01:49:23,440 --> 01:49:25,530
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你是登丹人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You are one of the Dunedain.</font>

1068
01:49:26,610 --> 01:49:29,700
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">努曼诺尔的后代  会很长寿
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A descendant of Numenor, blessed with long life.</font>

1069
01:49:30,950 --> 01:49:33,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">据说你的经历带有传奇色彩
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It was said that your race had passed into legend.</font>

1070
01:49:34,250 --> 01:49:36,040
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们当中很少人活了下来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There are few of us left.</font>

1071
01:49:36,210 --> 01:49:38,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">北方王国很久以前就被摧毁了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The Northern Kingdom was destroyed long ago.</font>

1072
01:49:39,750 --> 01:49:43,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">对不起  吃吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'm sorry. Please, eat.</font>

1073
01:49:57,810 --> 01:50:01,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">暮星的光芒不会减弱
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The light of the Evenstar does not wax and wane.</font>

1074
01:50:02,730 --> 01:50:06,150
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我想要给谁就给谁
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It is mine to give to whom I will.</font>

1075
01:50:07,990 --> 01:50:10,410
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就像我的心一样
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Like my heart.</font>

1076
01:50:11,830 --> 01:50:14,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快睡吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Go to sleep.</font>

1077
01:50:14,700 --> 01:50:17,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我已经睡着了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am asleep.</font>

1078
01:50:23,670 --> 01:50:25,630
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这只是个梦
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This is a dream.</font>

1079
01:50:27,840 --> 01:50:31,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那么这一定是美梦
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Then it is a good dream.</font>

1080
01:50:43,020 --> 01:50:45,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">睡吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Sleep.</font>

1081
01:51:10,240 --> 01:51:11,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你曾经说过...
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Minlû pedich nin..."</font>

1082
01:51:14,250 --> 01:51:16,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">该来的终会来的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"i aur hen telitha."</font>

1083
01:51:17,460 --> 01:51:20,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这不是结束...这只是开始
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"ú i vethed na i onnad."</font>

1084
01:51:20,250 --> 01:51:22,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你必须跟随佛罗多
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Boe bedich go Frodo."</font>

1085
01:51:23,130 --> 01:51:25,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那是你的宿命
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Han bâd lîn."</font>

1086
01:51:35,560 --> 01:51:38,340
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我看不见我的宿命
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Dolen i vad o nin."</font>

1087
01:51:39,020 --> 01:51:42,730
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它就在你脚下
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Si peliannen i vâd na dail lîn."</font>

1088
01:51:42,730 --> 01:51:46,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你没法逃避
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Siboe ú-dhannathach."</font>

1089
01:51:48,090 --> 01:51:50,010
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚文
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Arwen...</font>

1090
01:51:52,620 --> 01:51:54,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">如果你什么都不信...
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Ae ú-esteliach nad..."</font>

1091
01:51:55,290 --> 01:51:57,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就相信这个吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"estelio han."</font>

1092
01:51:58,540 --> 01:52:00,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">相信我们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"estelio ammen."</font>

1093
01:52:39,760 --> 01:52:41,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">她在哪里?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is she?</font>

1094
01:52:42,590 --> 01:52:45,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">给你那枚宝石的女人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The woman who gave you that jewel.</font>

1095
01:52:48,350 --> 01:52:51,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们的时代结束了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Our time here is ending.</font>

1096
01:52:51,810 --> 01:52:54,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚玟也要离开
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Arwen's time is ending.</font>

1097
01:52:55,350 --> 01:52:56,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让她走吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let her go.</font>

1098
01:52:56,770 --> 01:52:58,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让她坐船前往西方
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let her take the ship into the west.</font>

1099
01:52:58,980 --> 01:53:02,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让她带着对你的爱到海外仙境
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let her bear away her love for you to the Undying Lands.</font>

1100
01:53:02,190 --> 01:53:03,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">她对你的爱将永远长青
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There it will be ever green.</font>

1101
01:53:05,530 --> 01:53:07,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是她只有回忆
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But never more than memory.</font>

1102
01:53:09,150 --> 01:53:12,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我不会让我女儿留下来等死
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I will not leave my daughter here to die.</font>

1103
01:53:12,370 --> 01:53:15,990
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 她心存希望才会留下来的    - 她是为了你才留下来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- She stays because she still has hope.   - She stays for you.</font>

1104
01:53:16,160 --> 01:53:18,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">她应该跟她的族人在一起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">She belongs with her people.</font>

1105
01:54:06,750 --> 01:54:08,590
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你为什么要我走?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Why are you saying this?</font>

1106
01:54:10,170 --> 01:54:13,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我是凡人 你是精灵
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I am mortal. You are Elf-kind.</font>

1107
01:54:14,800 --> 01:54:17,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这只是一场梦
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It was a dream, Arwen.</font>

1108
01:54:17,890 --> 01:54:19,270
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一场美梦而已
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Nothing more.</font>

1109
01:54:20,640 --> 01:54:23,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">真不敢相信
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I don't believe you.</font>

1110
01:54:32,900 --> 01:54:34,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这属于你
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This belongs to you.</font>

1111
01:54:37,490 --> 01:54:39,040
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是送你的礼物
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It was a gift.</font>

1112
01:54:41,660 --> 01:54:43,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">留着它
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Keep it.</font>

1113
01:54:45,710 --> 01:54:46,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">大人?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My lord?</font>

1114
01:54:49,710 --> 01:54:54,260
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">她要跟其他的精灵到海外仙境
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">She is sailing to the Undying Lands with all that is left of her kin.</font>

1115
01:55:17,780 --> 01:55:18,800
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">怎么了?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What is it?</font>

1116
01:55:20,740 --> 01:55:22,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">-哈玛?      - 我不确定
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Hama?     - I'm not sure.</font>

1117
01:55:39,300 --> 01:55:41,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">狼骑士!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Wargs!</font>

1118
01:55:53,900 --> 01:55:55,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他是来探路的先锋!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A scout!</font>

1119
01:56:01,910 --> 01:56:04,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 怎么了? 那是什么?     - 狼骑士 我们受到攻击!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- What is it? What do you see?    - Warg! We're under attack!</font>

1120
01:56:05,670 --> 01:56:07,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">带他们离开这里!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Get them out of here!</font>

1121
01:56:12,630 --> 01:56:14,640
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">骑士全都到前锋!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">All riders to the head of the column.</font>

1122
01:56:15,390 --> 01:56:17,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快让我上去 我也是骑士
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Come on. Get me up here. I'm a rider.</font>

1123
01:56:17,560 --> 01:56:19,270
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">来吧!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Come on!</font>

1124
01:56:31,070 --> 01:56:33,530
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快带人民到圣盔谷 快去!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You must lead the people to Helm's Deep, and make haste.</font>

1125
01:56:33,740 --> 01:56:35,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 我可以作战      - 不行!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- I can fight.     - No!</font>

1126
01:56:37,910 --> 01:56:39,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你要为了我带他们去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You must do this, for me.</font>

1127
01:56:41,960 --> 01:56:43,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">跟我来!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Follow me!</font>

1128
01:56:47,090 --> 01:56:51,420
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 前进 我是说向前冲     - 快到低地
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Forward. I mean, charge forward.   - Make for the lower ground!</font>

1129
01:56:51,590 --> 01:56:54,260
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 很好 快呀     - 聚在一起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- That's it! Go on!     - Stay together!</font>

1130
01:58:06,500 --> 01:58:08,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快来领死吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Bring your pretty face to my ax.</font>

1131
01:58:11,590 --> 01:58:13,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那一只算我的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That one counts as mine!</font>

1132
01:58:29,900 --> 01:58:31,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">臭东西
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Stinking creature.</font>

1133
01:59:58,690 --> 02:00:00,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉冈!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Aragorn!</font>

1134
02:00:05,330 --> 02:00:06,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉冈?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Aragorn?</font>

1135
02:00:20,800 --> 02:00:23,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快说我就让你死得痛快
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Tell me what happened and I will ease your passing.</font>

1136
02:00:23,890 --> 02:00:25,300
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他...
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He's...</font>

1137
02:00:25,890 --> 02:00:27,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">死了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...dead.</font>

1138
02:00:28,140 --> 02:00:31,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他跌下悬崖
