</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Get the wounded on horses.</font>

1141
02:01:12,770 --> 02:01:15,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">艾辛格的恶狼会再回来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The wolves of Isengard will return.</font>

1142
02:01:16,350 --> 02:01:18,440
