</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Leave the dead.</font>

1143
02:01:25,860 --> 02:01:27,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">来吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Come.</font>

1144
02:01:37,540 --> 02:01:39,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 终于到了!     - 圣盔谷!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- At last!     - Helm's Deep.</font>

1145
02:01:39,250 --> 02:01:42,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">到了 圣盔谷
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There it is, Helm's Deep.</font>

1146
02:01:44,720 --> 02:01:46,550
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们安全了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We're safe!</font>

1147
02:01:48,050 --> 02:01:50,930
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">安全了 王女
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We're safe, my lady.</font>

1148
02:01:51,100 --> 02:01:52,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">谢谢
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

1149
02:02:36,680 --> 02:02:38,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 妈妈     - 伊欧参!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Mama!     - Eothain!</font>

1150
02:02:38,270 --> 02:02:39,730
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">弗雷达!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Freda!</font>

1151
02:02:45,490 --> 02:02:48,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 剩下的在哪儿?     - 只有这些了  女王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Where is the rest?   - This is all we could save, my lady.</font>

1152
02:02:52,200 --> 02:02:53,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">拿到洞里去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Take it to the caves.</font>

1153
02:02:53,700 --> 02:02:56,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">给国王让路
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Make way for the king.</font>

1154
02:02:57,580 --> 02:03:01,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">迎接希优顿 迎接骠骑王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Make way for Theoden.Make way for the king.</font>

1155
02:03:09,300 --> 02:03:13,010
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">好少人 回来的人好少
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">So few. So few of you have returned.</font>

1156
02:03:15,810 --> 02:03:18,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们的人民安全了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Our people are safe.</font>

1157
02:03:19,390 --> 02:03:21,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是却牺牲很多条人命
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We have paid for it with many lives.</font>

1158
02:03:22,810 --> 02:03:24,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的王女
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My lady.</font>

1159
02:03:28,070 --> 02:03:30,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉冈大人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Lord Aragorn...</font>

1160
02:03:30,490 --> 02:03:31,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他人呢?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...where is he?</font>

1161
02:03:33,740 --> 02:03:35,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他不在了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He fell.</font>

1162
02:03:57,930 --> 02:04:00,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">在城墙后方派重兵驻守
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Draw all our forces behind the wall.</font>

1163
02:04:01,060 --> 02:04:04,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">挡住城门  哨兵守住城池
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Bar the gate. And set a watch on the surround.</font>

1164
02:04:04,230 --> 02:04:07,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的主人 不能打仗的人怎么办? 女人和小孩
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What of those who cannot fight, my lord? The women and children?</font>

1165
02:04:07,530 --> 02:04:10,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">带他们进入洞穴
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Get them into the caves.</font>

1166
02:04:10,990 --> 02:04:15,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼别妄想攻下这座铜墙铁壁
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Saruman's arm will have grown long indeed if he thinks he can reach us here.</font>

1167
02:04:17,870 --> 02:04:21,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">圣盔谷只有一个弱点
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Helm 's Deep has one weakness.</font>

1168
02:04:21,460 --> 02:04:23,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它的外墙是巨石砌成
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Its outer wall is soild rock...</font>

1169
02:04:23,960 --> 02:04:27,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是它的基座有一条渠道
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...but for a small culvert at its base...</font>

1170
02:04:27,210 --> 02:04:30,010
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">只比排水管大一点
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...which is little more than a drain.</font>

1171
02:04:32,880 --> 02:04:37,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">怎么做 火怎么烧得了石头?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">How? How can fire undo stone?</font>

1172
02:04:37,220 --> 02:04:41,680
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你要用什么方法摧毁城墙?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What kind of device could bring down the wall?</font>

1173
02:04:45,310 --> 02:04:49,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">只要攻下城墙 圣盔谷就会瓦解
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">If the wall is breached, Helm's Deep will fall.</font>

1174
02:04:49,480 --> 02:04:53,030
