</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Even if it is breached, it would take a number beyond reckoning...</font>

1175
02:04:53,200 --> 02:04:55,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">才攻得进去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...thousands, to storm the Keep.</font>

1176
02:04:55,910 --> 02:04:57,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">成千上万名士兵
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Tens of thousands.</font>

1177
02:04:57,530 --> 02:05:01,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">大人 我们没有这种大军
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But, my lord, there is no such force.</font>

1178
02:05:13,550 --> 02:05:16,640
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一股新势力崛起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A new power is rising.</font>

1179
02:05:16,800 --> 02:05:19,810
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它即将获得胜利!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Its victory is at hand.</font>

1180
02:05:25,480 --> 02:05:27,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">今晚
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This night...</font>

1181
02:05:27,980 --> 02:05:32,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">洛汗人的鲜血将染红大地
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...the land will be stained with the blood of Rohan!</font>

1182
02:05:32,490 --> 02:05:35,820
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">向圣盔谷进军
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">March to Helm's Deep!</font>

1183
02:05:35,990 --> 02:05:39,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不能留下活口
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Leave none alive!</font>

1184
02:05:41,950 --> 02:05:44,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">开战!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">To war!</font>

1185
02:05:48,380 --> 02:05:52,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">人类将看不到明天的曙光
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There will be no dawn for Men.</font>

1186
02:06:10,020 --> 02:06:12,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">看 南方有烟硝升起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Look. There's smoke to the south.</font>

1187
02:06:12,320 --> 02:06:19,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">最近艾辛格一直有烟硝升起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There is always smoke rising from Isengard these days.</font>

1188
02:06:19,740 --> 02:06:21,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">艾辛格?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Isengard?</font>

1189
02:06:21,530 --> 02:06:23,410
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">很久以前
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There was a time...</font>

1190
02:06:23,750 --> 02:06:27,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼会来我的森林漫步
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...when Saruman would walk in my woods.</font>

1191
02:06:27,460 --> 02:06:30,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是现在他却满脑子都是钢铁
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But now he has a mind of metal...</font>

1192
02:06:31,500 --> 02:06:33,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">还有铁轮
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...and wheels.</font>

1193
02:06:34,670 --> 02:06:39,180
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他对大自然不再感兴趣
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He no longer cares for growing things.</font>

1194
02:06:39,340 --> 02:06:41,180
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那是什么?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What is it?</font>

1195
02:06:46,180 --> 02:06:48,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼的大军
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's Saruman's army.</font>

1196
02:06:48,560 --> 02:06:50,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">战争爆发了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The war has started.</font>

1197
02:07:28,480 --> 02:07:32,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">愿主神保佑你
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">May the grace of the Valar protect you.</font>

1198
02:08:05,100 --> 02:08:06,970
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">布理哥
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Brego.</font>

1199
02:08:33,120 --> 02:08:34,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚玟
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Arwen.</font>

1200
02:08:35,400 --> 02:08:37,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">是时候了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Tollen i lû."</font>

1201
02:08:39,370 --> 02:08:43,280
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">去维林诺的船就要开了...走吧 免得来不及
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"I chair gwannar na Valannor. Si bado, no círar..."</font>

1202
02:08:44,090 --> 02:08:45,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我做了决定
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I have made my choice.</font>

1203
02:08:52,310 --> 02:08:55,190
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他不会回来了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He is not coming back.</font>

1204
02:08:56,650 --> 02:08:59,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">没有希望为何还要留恋?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Why do you linger here when there is no hope?</font>

1205
02:09:00,900 --> 02:09:03,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">还是有希望
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There is still hope.</font>

1206
02:09:08,030 --> 02:09:11,830
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就算亚拉冈在战争中活下来你们还是会分开
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">If Aragorn survives this war, you will still be parted.</font>

1207
02:09:15,210 --> 02:09:18,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就算亚拉冈打败索伦成为国王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">If Sauron is defeated and Aragorn made king...</font>

1208
02:09:18,340 --> 02:09:20,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">而你的愿望也都实现
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...and all that you hope for comes true...</font>

1209
02:09:21,010 --> 02:09:25,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他还是逃不了死亡的命运
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...you will still have to taste the bitterness of mortality.</font>

1210
02:09:26,010 --> 02:09:28,970
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不管是战死或是老死
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Whether by the sword or the slow decay of time...</font>

1211
02:09:29,180 --> 02:09:32,140
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉冈都难逃一死
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...Aragorn will die.</font>

1212
02:09:34,980 --> 02:09:37,480
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你将得不到安慰
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And there will be no comfort for you...</font>

1213
02:09:37,690 --> 02:09:41,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">永远为他的死伤心难过
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...no comfort to ease the pain of his passing.</font>

1214
02:09:44,700 --> 02:09:47,410
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他死了以后
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He will come to death...</font>

1215
02:09:47,570 --> 02:09:50,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">身为国王的英勇形象
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...an image of the splendor of the kings of Men...</font>

1216
02:09:50,200 --> 02:09:54,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">将留在世人心中永不磨灭
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...in glory undimmed before the breaking of the world.</font>

1217
02:10:04,130 --> 02:10:08,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但是你 我的爱女
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But you, my daughter...</font>

1218
02:10:08,890 --> 02:10:13,930
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">将活在恒久不变的黑暗中
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...you will linger on in darkness and in doubt...</font>

1219
02:10:14,100 --> 02:10:18,190
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就像没有星光的冬夜
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...as nightfall in winter that comes without a star.</font>

1220
02:10:20,570 --> 02:10:22,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你将满怀伤悲
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Here you will dwell...</font>

1221
02:10:23,150 --> 02:10:28,070
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">住在一天一天干枯的老树下
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...bound to your grief under the fading trees...</font>

1222
02:10:29,780 --> 02:10:31,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">直到世界改变
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...until all the world is changed...</font>

1223
02:10:31,950 --> 02:10:36,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">虚度你漫长的一生
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...and the long years of your life are utterly spent.</font>

1224
02:10:44,960 --> 02:10:46,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚玟
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Arwen.</font>

1225
02:10:52,760 --> 02:10:55,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你在这儿什么也没有
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There is nothing for you here...</font>

1226
02:10:55,730 --> 02:10:57,810
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">只有死亡
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...only death.</font>

1227
02:11:18,450 --> 02:11:21,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你还是会爱着我的吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Ah im, ú'erin veleth lîn?"</font>

1228
02:11:23,200 --> 02:11:24,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">当然会的 父亲
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">"Gerich veleth nîn, ada."</font>

1229
02:12:31,280 --> 02:12:34,910
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">敌人的力量越来越强大
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The power of the enemy is growing.</font>

1230
02:12:35,070 --> 02:12:37,700
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">索伦将利用他的傀儡萨鲁曼
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Sauron will use his puppet, Saruman...</font>

1231
02:12:37,870 --> 02:12:41,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">消灭洛汗人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...to destroy the people of Rohan.</font>

1232
02:12:43,330 --> 02:12:46,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">艾辛格出动邪恶大军
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Isengard has been unleashed.</font>

1233
02:12:51,300 --> 02:12:54,680
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">邪眼把目标转向刚铎
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The Eye of Sauron now turns to Gondor...</font>

1234
02:12:55,800 --> 02:12:58,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">人类最后的自由国土
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...the last free kingdom of Men.</font>

1235
02:12:58,970 --> 02:13:03,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他将迅雷不及掩耳地进攻刚铎
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">His war on this country will come swiftly.</font>

1236
02:13:07,070 --> 02:13:10,190
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他感到魔戒离他很近
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He senses the Ring is close.</font>

1237
02:13:10,360 --> 02:13:13,820
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">魔戒持有者的意志越来越薄弱
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The strength of the Ring-bearer is failing.</font>

1238
02:13:13,990 --> 02:13:18,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">佛罗多的内心深处知道
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">In his heart, Frodo begins to understand...</font>

1239
02:13:19,580 --> 02:13:23,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这场旅程将夺去他的生命
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...the quest will claim his life.</font>

1240
02:13:23,620 --> 02:13:25,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你很清楚
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You know this.</font>

1241
02:13:26,420 --> 02:13:29,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你也预见到了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You have foreseen It.</font>

1242
02:13:31,380 --> 02:13:34,800
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是我们必须冒的险
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It Is the risk we all took.</font>

1243
02:13:39,140 --> 02:13:43,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">当邪恶力量聚集  魔戒的意志力就会加强
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">In the gathering dark, the will of the Ring grows strong.</font>

1244
02:13:44,520 --> 02:13:48,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它一心一意想回到人类手上
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It works hard now to find its way back Into the hands of Men.</font>

1245
02:13:49,110 --> 02:13:54,570
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">因为人类很容易受到它的诱惑
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Men, who are so easily seduced by Its power.</font>

1246
02:13:54,780 --> 02:13:58,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">年轻的刚铎将军只要伸出手
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The young captain of Gondor has but to extend his hand...</font>

1247
02:13:58,580 --> 02:14:02,620
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希望将魔戒占为己有  整个世界就会沦陷
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...take the Ring for his own, and the world will fall.</font>

1248
02:14:05,080 --> 02:14:06,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就快了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It is close now.</font>

1249
02:14:07,080 --> 02:14:11,340
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就快达成他的目标
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">So close to achieving its goal.</font>

1250
02:14:14,470 --> 02:14:18,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">索伦即将奴役世上所有生物
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">For Sauron will have dominion over all life on this Earth...</font>

1251
02:14:18,260 --> 02:14:22,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">甚至带来中土世界的灭亡
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...even unto to the ending of the world.</font>

1252
02:14:24,230 --> 02:14:26,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">精灵的时代
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The time of the Elves...</font>

1253
02:14:26,270 --> 02:14:28,190
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">已经结束了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...is over.</font>

1254
02:14:29,020 --> 02:14:32,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们该让中土世界自生自灭?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Do we leave Middle-earth to Its fate?</font>

1255
02:14:34,610 --> 02:14:37,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">或是让他们孤军奋战?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Do we let them stand alone?</font>

1256
02:14:42,410 --> 02:14:43,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">有什么消息?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What news?</font>

1257
02:14:44,030 --> 02:14:46,830
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">据报萨鲁曼向洛汗国进攻
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Our scouts report Saruman has attacked Rohan.</font>

1258
02:14:47,000 --> 02:14:49,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希优顿率领人民逃到圣盔谷
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Theoden's people have fled to Helm's Deep.</font>

1259
02:14:50,040 --> 02:14:54,040
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们必须守住边境 法拉墨  半兽人蠢蠢欲动
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But we must look to our own borders. Faramir, Orcs are on the move.</font>

1260
02:14:54,250 --> 02:14:56,630
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">索伦在召集大军
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Sauron is marshaling an army.</font>

1261
02:14:56,960 --> 02:14:59,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">野人部落和南蛮族聚集在黑门
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Easterlings and Southrons are at the Black Gate.</font>

1262
02:14:59,260 --> 02:15:02,680
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 有多少?     - 几千人 每天都在增加
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- How many?     - Some thousands. More come every day.</font>

1263
02:15:03,760 --> 02:15:07,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 谁驻守在北边河流?     - 奥斯吉力斯的五百名精兵
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Who's covering the river to the north?   - We pulled 500 men at Osgiliath.</font>

1264
02:15:07,560 --> 02:15:10,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">受到攻击绝对抵挡不了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">If their city is attacked, we won't hold it.</font>

1265
02:15:12,730 --> 02:15:14,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼从艾辛格发动攻击
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Saruman attacks from Isengard.</font>

1266
02:15:15,110 --> 02:15:17,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">从魔多出发
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Sauron from Mordor.</font>

1267
02:15:19,110 --> 02:15:22,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">会从正面攻击人类
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The fight will come to Men on both fronts.</font>

1268
02:15:22,490 --> 02:15:24,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">刚铎现在正虚弱
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Gondor is weak.</font>

1269
02:15:24,370 --> 02:15:27,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼很快便会攻打我们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Sauron will strike us soon.</font>

1270
02:15:28,240 --> 02:15:30,120
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">将会是一场硬仗
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And he will strike hard.</font>

1271
02:15:30,540 --> 02:15:34,630
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他知道现在的我们无力抵抗
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He knows now we do not have the strength to repel him.</font>

1272
02:15:48,510 --> 02:15:50,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的手下说你们俩是间谍
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My men tell me that you are Orc spies.</font>

1273
02:15:50,930 --> 02:15:53,650
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">间谍? 先等一等
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Spies? Now wait just a minute.</font>

1274
02:15:53,810 --> 02:15:56,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你们不是间谍是什么?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Well, if you're not spies, then who are you?</font>

1275
02:16:02,990 --> 02:16:04,700
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快说
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Speak.</font>

1276
02:16:05,820 --> 02:16:08,410
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们是夏尔来的哈比人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We are Hobbits of the Shire.</font>

1277
02:16:08,740 --> 02:16:11,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我的名字是佛罗多巴金斯  这是山姆卫斯詹吉
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Frodo Baggins is my name, and this is Samwise Gamgee.</font>

1278
02:16:12,210 --> 02:16:13,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你的保镖吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Your bodyguard?</font>

1279
02:16:13,920 --> 02:16:15,670
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他的园丁
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">His gardener.</font>

1280
02:16:16,330 --> 02:16:18,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你们鬼鬼祟祟的朋友呢?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And where is your skulking friend?</font>

1281
02:16:19,840 --> 02:16:22,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">滑不溜丢的小子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That gangrel creature.</font>

1282
02:16:22,470 --> 02:16:24,430
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那个丑八怪
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He had an ill-favored look.</font>

1283
02:16:26,180 --> 02:16:28,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">没有别人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There was no other.</font>

1284
02:16:32,180 --> 02:16:34,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们七个人从瑞文戴尔出发
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We set out from Rivendell with seven companions.</font>

1285
02:16:37,860 --> 02:16:40,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们在摩瑞亚失去一个
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">One we lost in Moria...</font>

1286
02:16:41,990 --> 02:16:43,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">有两个也是哈比人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...two were my kin...</font>

1287
02:16:43,700 --> 02:16:47,410
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">还有一个矮人  一个精灵和两个人类
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...a Dwarf there was also. And an Elf and two Men.</font>

1288
02:16:47,620 --> 02:16:51,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉松之子亚拉冈和钢铎人波罗莫
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Aragorn, son of Arathorn, and Boromir of Gondor.</font>

1289
02:16:56,540 --> 02:16:58,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你是波罗莫的朋友?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You're a friend of Boromir?</font>

1290
02:17:00,710 --> 02:17:02,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">对
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

1291
02:17:03,300 --> 02:17:04,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">至少我是这么想
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">For my part.</font>

1292
02:17:10,890 --> 02:17:13,850
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那听到他的死讯你一定会很难过
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It will grieve you then to learn that he is dead.</font>

1293
02:17:15,890 --> 02:17:17,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">死了?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Dead?</font>

1294
02:17:17,560 --> 02:17:19,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">怎么会? 几时?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">How? When?</font>

1295
02:17:19,860 --> 02:17:22,480
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你是他同伴  你倒是告诉我
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">As one of his companions, I'd hoped you would tell me.</font>

1296
02:17:22,820 --> 02:17:26,650
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">如果波罗莫出事了  请告诉我
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">If something has happened to Boromir, we would have you tell us.</font>

1297
02:17:29,410 --> 02:17:35,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他的号角在河里洗了6天了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">His horn washed up upon the riverbank, about six days past.</font>

1298
02:17:36,080 --> 02:17:39,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">已经分成了两块
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It was cloven in two.</font>

1299
02:17:40,750 --> 02:17:44,170
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我从内心知道  还不止这些
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But more than this, I know it in my heart.</font>

1300
02:17:46,220 --> 02:17:48,010
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他是我的兄长
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He was my brother.</font>

1301
02:18:36,980 --> 02:18:39,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">波罗莫
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Boromir!</font>

1302
02:18:40,480 --> 02:18:42,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">波罗莫
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Boromir!</font>

1303
02:18:46,570 --> 02:18:50,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这城市曾经是我们王国的明珠
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This city was once the jewel of our kingdom.</font>

1304
02:18:50,490 --> 02:18:54,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">充满光明 美景和音乐
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A place of light and beauty and music.</font>

1305
02:18:54,330 --> 02:18:56,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这些应该重现!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And so it shall be once more!</font>

1306
02:18:59,250 --> 02:19:01,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">要让魔多的军队知道
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let the armies of Mordor know this</font>

1307
02:19:02,080 --> 02:19:06,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们的人民不会再次落入敌人手中
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Never again will the land of my people fall into enemy hands.</font>

1308
02:19:10,260 --> 02:19:15,930
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">奥斯吉力亚斯城已经被刚铎收复!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This city of Osgiliath has been reclaimed for Gondor!</font>

1309
02:19:16,310 --> 02:19:18,270
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 为了刚铎!     - 为了刚铎!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- For Gondor!     - For Gondor!</font>

1310
02:19:18,430 --> 02:19:21,270
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 为了刚铎!     - 为了刚铎!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- For Gondor!     - For Gondor!</font>

1311
02:19:29,990 --> 02:19:32,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不错的演讲  精彩 精练
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Good speech. Nice and short.</font>

1312
02:19:32,950 --> 02:19:35,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这样就有更多时间喝酒!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Leaves more time for drinking!</font>

1313
02:19:36,160 --> 02:19:40,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让我们开怀畅饮!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Break out the ale! These men are thirsty!</font>

1314
02:19:43,790 --> 02:19:45,960
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">记住今天  兄弟们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Remember today, little brother.</font>

1315
02:19:46,130 --> 02:19:49,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">今天  生命是美好的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Today, life is good.</font>

1316
02:19:53,300 --> 02:19:54,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">什么?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What?</font>

1317
02:19:55,260 --> 02:19:56,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他在这里
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He's here.</font>

1318
02:19:59,930 --> 02:20:01,770
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他就不能给我们短暂的和平吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">One moment of peace, can he not give us that?</font>

1319
02:20:01,930 --> 02:20:02,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他在哪儿?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is he?</font>

1320
02:20:03,140 --> 02:20:06,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">刚铎的人在哪儿? 第一个呢?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is Gondor's finest? Where's my first-born?</font>

1321
02:20:07,190 --> 02:20:08,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">父亲!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Father!</font>

1322
02:20:13,740 --> 02:20:16,120
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们说你独自征服了他们的军队
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They say you vanquished the enemy almost single-handedly.</font>

