</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Stop it!</font>

1432
02:29:48,000 --> 02:29:49,080
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让他走!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Leave him alone.</font>

1433
02:29:50,420 --> 02:29:52,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你不明白吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Don't you understand?</font>

1434
02:29:54,210 --> 02:29:56,130
