</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That's where we're going, into Mordor.</font>

1436
02:29:59,680 --> 02:30:01,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">把它丢进末日火山烈焰
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">To the Mountain of Fire!</font>

1437
02:30:02,430 --> 02:30:05,520
