</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Please. It's such a burden.</font>

1439
02:30:10,900 --> 02:30:12,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你不肯帮他吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Will you not help him?</font>

1440
02:30:14,360 --> 02:30:16,240
