<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你看起来好惨
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You look terrible.</font>

1450
02:32:54,850 --> 02:32:56,850
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一支大军?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A great host, you say?</font>

1451
02:32:57,060 --> 02:32:59,730
