</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">To destroy the world of Men.</font>

1456
02:33:16,620 --> 02:33:18,630
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们入夜就会攻到
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They will be here by nightfall.</font>

1457
02:33:24,470 --> 02:33:25,760
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让他们来吧!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let them come!</font>

1458
02:33:27,300 --> 02:33:30,010
