</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I want every man and strong lad able to bear arms...</font>

1459
02:33:30,220 --> 02:33:33,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">佩带武器 今晚准备迎敌
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...to be ready for battle by nightfall.</font>

1460
