</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...homes rebuilt.</font>

1472
02:34:30,110 --> 02:34:32,700
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们在这座铜墙铁壁内
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Within these walls...</font>

1473
02:34:33,120 --> 02:34:34,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">撑得绝对比他们久
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...we will outlast them.</font>

1474
