02:37:15,150 --> 02:37:17,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">该不该参战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...will go to war.</font>

1514
02:37:26,710 --> 02:37:29,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">撤退 快进洞穴!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Move back! Move to the caves!</font>

1515
02:37:32,250 --> 02:37:34,300
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">继续走 快点!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Come on, people! Quickly, now!</font>

1516
02:37:34,720 --> 02:37:37,010
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">沿着城墙储备
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We'll place the reserves along the wall.</font>

1517
02:37:37,180 --> 02:37:39,430
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">可以从门上面支援弓箭手
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They can support the archers from above the gate.</font>

1518
02:37:39,600 --> 02:37:42,720
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉冈  你需要休息
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Aragorn, you must rest.</font>

1519
02:37:42,890 --> 02:37:45,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">半死对我们没用
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You're no use to us half alive.</font>

1520
02:37:45,770 --> 02:37:46,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">亚拉冈
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Aragorn!</font>

1521
02:37:50,360 --> 02:37:53,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我会和女人们一起到洞里去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'm to be sent with the women into the caves.</font>

1522
02:37:53,610 --> 02:37:55,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是一个光荣的机会
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That is an honorable charge.</font>

1523
02:37:55,440 --> 02:37:58,320
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">照顾孩子们  寻找食物  等待勇士们归来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">To mind the children, to find food and bedding when the men return.</font>

1524
02:37:58,490 --> 02:38:00,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那里的名声怎么样?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What renown is there in that?</font>

1525
02:38:00,320 --> 02:38:04,040
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">女王  这是英勇而不是为了名声
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My lady, a time may come for valor without renown.</font>

1526
02:38:04,330 --> 02:38:07,120
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">谁负责最后防线?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Who then will your people look to in the last defense?</font>

1527
02:38:07,290 --> 02:38:11,460
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 让我站到你那边     - 不是我的力量可以决定的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Let me stand at your side.  - It is not in my power to command it.</font>

1528
02:38:12,820 --> 02:38:14,800
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你不能命令其他人留下!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You do not command the others to stay!</font>

1529
02:38:15,440 --> 02:38:18,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们和你一起战斗因为他们不想和你分开
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They fight beside you because they would not be parted from you.</font>

1530
02:38:20,510 --> 02:38:22,680
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">因为他们热爱你
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Because they love you.</font>

1531
02:38:29,850 --> 02:38:31,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">对不起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'm sorry.</font>

1532
02:39:37,250 --> 02:39:40,510
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">农夫 老人 小孩
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Farmers, farriers, stable boys.</font>

1533
02:39:41,590 --> 02:39:43,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这些人根本无法作战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">These are no soldiers.</font>

1534
02:39:45,640 --> 02:39:49,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 他们多半见不到冬天了     - 人太少了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Most have seen too many winters.     - Or too few.</font>

1535
02:39:53,060 --> 02:39:55,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">看看他们  他们的恐惧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Look at them. They're frightened.</font>

1536
02:39:56,110 --> 02:39:57,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">从他们眼中你可以看出来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I can see it in their eyes.</font>

1537
02:40:18,590 --> 02:40:20,760
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那我也该跟着他们一起牺牲
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Then I shall die as one of them!</font>

1538
02:40:27,220 --> 02:40:29,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让他去吧  伙计
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let him go, lad.</font>

1539
02:40:29,640 --> 02:40:31,600
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让他去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let him be.</font>

1540
02:40:33,060 --> 02:40:38,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">会使剑的人都去领武器了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Every villager able to wield a sword has been sent to the armoury.</font>

1541
02:40:42,780 --> 02:40:44,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">王上?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My lord?</font>

1542
02:40:46,740 --> 02:40:49,290
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">加姆林 我是谁?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Who am I, Gamling?</font>

1543
02:40:52,660 --> 02:40:56,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">您是我们的国王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You are our king, sire.</font>

1544
02:40:59,590 --> 02:41:02,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你相信你的国王吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And do you trust your king?</font>

1545
02:41:04,380 --> 02:41:10,510
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">王上 您的士兵都将追随您
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Your men, my lord will follow you to whatever end.</font>

1546
02:41:17,440 --> 02:41:19,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">无论死活
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">To whatever end.</font>

1547
02:41:29,200 --> 02:41:32,750
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">骠悍的战马和骑士在哪里?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is the horse and the rider?</font>

1548
02:41:32,910 --> 02:41:36,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">胜利的号角在哪里?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where is the horn that was blowing?</font>

1549
02:41:37,500 --> 02:41:41,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它们早就消失了  就像落在高山的雨滴
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They have passed like rain on the mountains.</font>

1550
02:41:42,880 --> 02:41:46,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">或是拂过草原的微风
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Like wind in the meadow.</font>

1551
02:41:49,800 --> 02:41:53,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">昔日的荣耀就像太阳西下
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The days have gone down in the West...</font>

1552
02:41:54,270 --> 02:41:56,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">黯然消失在山后
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...behind the hills...</font>

1553
02:41:58,810 --> 02:42:00,440
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">被黑暗笼罩
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...into Shadow.</font>

1554
02:42:08,910 --> 02:42:12,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">怎么会变成这样?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">How did it come to this?</font>

1555
02:42:33,640 --> 02:42:35,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">已经很长时间了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's been going for hours.</font>

1556
02:42:36,640 --> 02:42:39,020
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们肯定已经做出决定了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They must have decided something by now.</font>

1557
02:42:39,190 --> 02:42:43,270
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">决定? 没有
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Decided? No.</font>

1558
02:42:43,440 --> 02:42:48,570
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们刚道完
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We only just finished saying...</font>

1559
02:42:49,780 --> 02:42:51,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">早安
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...good morning.</font>

1560
02:42:53,030 --> 02:42:56,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">但现在是半夜啊
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But it's nighttime already.</font>

1561
02:42:56,410 --> 02:42:58,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你们不能没完没了啊
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You can't take forever.</font>

1562
02:42:59,210 --> 02:43:01,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">别着急
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Don't be hasty.</font>

1563
02:43:01,710 --> 02:43:04,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们没时间了!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We're running out of time!</font>

1564
02:43:07,130 --> 02:43:10,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快 快到外墙
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Move! Move to the outer wall.</font>

1565
02:43:27,650 --> 02:43:28,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">把剑给我
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Give me your sword.</font>

1566
02:43:38,500 --> 02:43:39,620
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你叫什么?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What is your name?</font>

1567
02:43:40,160 --> 02:43:42,500
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">哈拉斯  哈玛之子
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Haleth, son of Hama, my lord.</font>

1568
02:43:44,670 --> 02:43:47,300
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">大家都说我们活不过今晚
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The men are saying we will not live out the night.</font>

1569
02:43:49,260 --> 02:43:51,220
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们说没有希望了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They say that it is hopeless.</font>

1570
02:44:09,070 --> 02:44:10,690
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是把好剑
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">This is a good sword.</font>

1571
02:44:12,740 --> 02:44:15,070
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">哈玛之子哈拉斯
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Haleth, son of Hama...</font>

1572
02:44:19,410 --> 02:44:21,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">永远都有希望
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...there is always hope.</font>

1573
02:44:44,520 --> 02:44:47,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们相信你 你也没令人失望
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We have trusted you this far. You have not led us astray.</font>

1574
02:44:48,070 --> 02:44:49,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">原谅我
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Forgive me.</font>

1575
02:44:49,780 --> 02:44:51,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我不该绝望
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I was wrong to despair.</font>

1576
02:45:00,410 --> 02:45:03,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">还来的及改改这身锁子甲
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We had time, I'd get this adjusted.</font>

1577
02:45:06,710 --> 02:45:08,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">胸口这儿有点紧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's a little tight across the chest.</font>

1578
02:45:14,930 --> 02:45:16,930
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那不是半兽人号角
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That is no Orc horn.</font>

1579
02:45:22,600 --> 02:45:24,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快去叫国王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Send for the king.</font>

1580
02:45:24,600 --> 02:45:28,190
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 打开大门!     - 打开大门!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Open the gate!     - Open up the gate!</font>

1581
02:45:59,800 --> 02:46:01,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这怎么可能?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">How is this possible?</font>

1582
02:46:02,470 --> 02:46:06,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我带来爱隆王的信息
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I bring word from Elrond of Rivendell.</font>

1583
02:46:06,310 --> 02:46:09,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">精灵曾和人类结为同盟
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">An alliance once existed between Elves and Men.</font>

1584
02:46:10,230 --> 02:46:14,440
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">在很久以前并肩作战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Long ago we fought and died together.</font>

1585
02:46:16,780 --> 02:46:19,660
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们是来实践我们的盟约的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We come to honor that allegiance.</font>

1586
02:46:28,170 --> 02:46:30,080
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">太欢迎了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You are most welcome.</font>

1587
02:46:35,460 --> 02:46:39,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们很荣幸再跟人类并肩作战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We are proud to fight alongside Men once more.</font>

1588
02:47:13,040 --> 02:47:16,340
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你挑的什么烂位置
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You could have picked a better spot.</font>

1589
02:47:21,220 --> 02:47:25,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希望你的好运气能撑过今晚
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Well, lad, whatever luck you live by, let's hope it lasts the night.</font>

1590
02:47:31,560 --> 02:47:33,360
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你的朋友都来了 亚拉冈
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Your friends are with you, Aragorn.</font>

1591
02:47:34,020 --> 02:47:36,480
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">希望他们熬得过今晚
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let's hope they last the night.</font>

1592
02:49:17,920 --> 02:49:20,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 发生什么事?     - 你要我说给你听?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- What's happening out there?   - Shall I describe it to you?</font>

1593
02:49:22,010 --> 02:49:23,800
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">还是替你找垫脚箱?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Or would you like me to find you a box?</font>

1594
02:50:26,990 --> 02:50:28,780
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">开战了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">So it begins.</font>

1595
02:50:55,600 --> 02:50:56,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">有没有射中?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Did they hit anything?</font>

1596
02:50:57,640 --> 02:50:59,650
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">齐射
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Give them a volley.</font>

1597
02:50:59,810 --> 02:51:01,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 放箭!     - 放箭!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- Fire!     - Fire!</font>

1598
02:51:17,660 --> 02:51:19,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">把他们送来领死  来啊!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Send them to me! Come on!</font>

1599
02:51:40,060 --> 02:51:41,150
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">很好!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Good!</font>

1600
02:51:47,990 --> 02:51:50,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">剑! 剑!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Swords! Swords!</font>

1601
02:52:29,070 --> 02:52:31,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">勒苟拉斯! 我痛宰了两个!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Legolas! Two already!</font>

1602
02:52:31,360 --> 02:52:33,490
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我杀了17个了!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'm on 17!</font>

1603
02:52:33,700 --> 02:52:36,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我可不能输给尖耳朵的家伙!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'll have no pointy-ear outscoring me!</font>

1604
02:52:43,000 --> 02:52:44,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">19!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Nineteen!</font>

1605
02:53:10,730 --> 02:53:12,150
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">梅里
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Merry.</font>

1606
02:53:16,570 --> 02:53:20,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们同意了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">We have just agreed.</font>

1607
02:53:30,420 --> 02:53:31,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">同意什么?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Yes?</font>

1608
02:53:33,380 --> 02:53:37,550
