03:06:35,400 --> 03:06:38,280
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">越危险的地方  越是安全
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The closer we are to danger, the farther we are from harm.</font>

1705
03:06:38,290 --> 03:06:40,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他一定料想不到
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's the last thing he'll expect.</font>

1706
03:06:42,480 --> 03:06:45,520
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我不太明白
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">That doesn't make sense to me.</font>

1707
03:06:45,690 --> 03:06:49,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不过你们个子很小
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But then you are very small.</font>

1708
03:06:50,240 --> 03:06:51,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">也许你们是对的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Perhaps you're right.</font>

1709
03:06:54,660 --> 03:06:56,120
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就南边吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">South it is, then.</font>

1710
03:06:57,660 --> 03:07:01,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">抓紧了 小哈比人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Hold on, little Shirelings.</font>

1711
03:07:03,040 --> 03:07:05,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我一向都喜欢往南走
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I always like going south.</font>

1712
03:07:06,000 --> 03:07:10,300
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就好像下坡一样
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Somehow it feels like going downhill.</font>

1713
03:07:10,880 --> 03:07:13,340
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你疯啦? 我们会被逮到
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Are you mad? We'll be caught.</font>

1714
03:07:13,510 --> 03:07:15,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">才不会
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">No, we won't.</font>

1715
03:07:16,180 --> 03:07:18,470
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这次不会
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Not this time.</font>

1716
03:07:25,150 --> 03:07:26,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你看!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Look!</font>

1717
03:07:27,820 --> 03:07:30,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">奥斯吉力亚斯在燃烧!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Osgiliath burns!</font>

1718
03:07:30,400 --> 03:07:31,820
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">魔多大军攻来了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Mordor has come.</font>

1719
03:07:32,990 --> 03:07:35,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">魔戒也救不了刚铎
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The Ring will not save Gondor.</font>

1720
03:07:36,700 --> 03:07:38,910
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它只有毁灭的力量
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It has only the power to destroy.</font>

1721
03:07:39,750 --> 03:07:41,160
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">求求你
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Please...</font>

1722
03:07:41,370 --> 03:07:43,000
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">让我走
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...let me go.</font>

1723
03:07:49,090 --> 03:07:50,510
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快点!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Faramir!</font>

1724
03:07:50,670 --> 03:07:53,130
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">法拉墨 你一定要让我走!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You must let me go!</font>

1725
03:07:53,590 --> 03:07:57,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">那一群田鼠
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">And those little family of field mice...</font>

1726
03:07:57,220 --> 03:08:00,060
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它们爬到我身上好痒哦
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...that climb up sometimes, and they tickle me awfully.</font>

1727
03:08:00,810 --> 03:08:04,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它们老是爬到
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They're always trying to get somewhere where they...</font>

1728
03:08:15,280 --> 03:08:18,240
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这儿有很多树是我的朋友
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Many of these trees were my friends.</font>

1729
03:08:18,910 --> 03:08:23,540
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们还是种子时我就认识他们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Creatures I had known from nut and acorn.</font>

1730
03:08:24,750 --> 03:08:25,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">很遗憾 树须
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">I'm sorry, Treebeard.</font>

1731
03:08:26,080 --> 03:08:28,880
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们有自己的声音
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They had voices of their own.</font>

1732
03:08:31,130 --> 03:08:33,670
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">萨鲁曼
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Saruman.</font>

1733
03:08:34,050 --> 03:08:37,090
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一个巫师不该这么做!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A wizard should know better!</font>

1734
03:08:51,320 --> 03:08:54,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">没有更强烈的字眼
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There is no curse in Elvish...</font>

1735
03:08:55,150 --> 03:08:57,820
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">在精灵语  树人语或是人类语中
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...Entish or the tongues of Men...</font>

1736
03:08:57,990 --> 03:09:00,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">来诅咒这种恶行
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...for this treachery.</font>

1737
03:09:01,790 --> 03:09:04,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">看啊  这些树在动!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Look! The trees! They're moving!</font>

1738
03:09:09,290 --> 03:09:10,500
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们要去哪儿?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Where are they going?</font>

1739
03:09:11,050 --> 03:09:14,260
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们和兽人有些帐要算
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They have business with the Orcs.</font>

1740
03:09:14,760 --> 03:09:21,810
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我今晚要用巨石和岩石摧毁艾辛格
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">My business is with Isengard tonight with rock and stone.</font>

1741
03:09:45,700 --> 03:09:46,830
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">好啊
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

1742
03:09:47,960 --> 03:09:49,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">来吧 朋友们
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Come, my friends.</font>

1743
03:09:50,710 --> 03:09:54,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">树人要开战了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The Ents are going to war.</font>

1744
03:09:55,090 --> 03:09:56,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们很可能
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It is likely...</font>

1745
03:09:57,010 --> 03:10:00,550
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">会走向灭亡之路
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...that we go to our doom.</font>

1746
03:10:01,970 --> 03:10:06,980
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是树人最后的一战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Last march of the Ents.</font>

1747
03:10:55,110 --> 03:10:58,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">半兽人占领了东岸  他们的数量太多
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Faramir! Orcs have taken the eastern shore. Their numbers are too great.</font>

1748
03:10:59,030 --> 03:11:01,070
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">到晚上我们就会溃不成军
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">By nightfall we will be overrun.</font>

1749
03:11:03,870 --> 03:11:05,330
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">佛罗多先生?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Mr. Frodo?</font>

1750
03:11:05,620 --> 03:11:09,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">它在召唤他  邪眼就快看到我
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It's calling to him, Sam. His Eye is almost on me.</font>

1751
03:11:09,910 --> 03:11:12,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">撑着点 佛罗多先生你不会有事的
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Hold on, Mr. Frodo. You'll be all right.</font>

1752
03:11:26,760 --> 03:11:28,140
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">把他带去见父王
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Take them to my father.</font>

1753
03:11:29,730 --> 03:11:32,690
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">就说法拉墨送上大礼
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Tell him Faramir sends a mighty gift.</font>

1754
03:11:35,110 --> 03:11:38,150
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">一个足以扭转局势的武器
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">A weapon that will change our fortunes in this war.</font>

1755
03:11:39,280 --> 03:11:41,950
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你想知道波罗莫的遭遇吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Do you want to know what happened to Boromir?</font>

1756
03:11:42,610 --> 03:11:45,370
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你想知道你兄长为什么死吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You want to know why your brother died?</font>

1757
03:11:45,870 --> 03:11:49,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他誓言保护佛罗多  却想夺走魔戒
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He tried to take the Ring from Frodo after swearing an oath to protect him!</font>

1758
03:11:49,790 --> 03:11:51,710
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">想杀了他!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">He tried to kill him!</font>

1759
03:11:51,870 --> 03:11:54,210
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">魔戒把你兄长逼疯!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The Ring drove your brother mad!</font>

1760
03:11:54,960 --> 03:11:56,840
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">小心!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Watch out!</font>

1761
03:12:07,760 --> 03:12:08,890
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">佛罗多先生?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Mr. Frodo?</font>

1762
03:12:11,520 --> 03:12:13,350
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们在这儿
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They're here.</font>

1763
03:12:16,480 --> 03:12:18,940
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们来了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They've come.</font>

1764
03:12:21,530 --> 03:12:23,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">戒灵!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Nazg鹟!</font>

1765
03:12:45,510 --> 03:12:47,640
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">待在这儿 躲起来
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Stay here. Keep out of sight.</font>

1766
03:12:49,470 --> 03:12:51,680
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">快找掩护!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Take cover!</font>

1767
03:13:09,030 --> 03:13:10,620
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">堡垒被攻陷
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The fortress is taken.</font>

1768
03:13:11,370 --> 03:13:12,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我们输了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">It is over.</font>

1769
03:13:12,750 --> 03:13:16,670
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">你说这座堡垒绝不会沦陷  他们会奋战到底
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">You said this fortress would never fall while your men defend it.</font>

1770
03:13:16,870 --> 03:13:19,790
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们还在浴血奋战
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They still defend it. They have died defending it.</font>

1771
03:13:22,550 --> 03:13:23,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们攻进来了!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They're breaking in!</font>

1772
03:13:26,550 --> 03:13:29,050
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">他们破门而入了!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">They're past the door!</font>

1773
03:13:32,430 --> 03:13:36,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">女人小孩没办法逃出去吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Is there no other way for the women and children to get out of the caves?</font>

1774
03:13:39,190 --> 03:13:41,110
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">没别的路了吗?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Is there no other way?</font>

1775
03:13:42,690 --> 03:13:45,740
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">有一条通道 直接到山上
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">There is one passage. It leads into the mountains.</font>

1776
03:13:46,400 --> 03:13:48,610
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">不过逃不了多远  到处都有强兽人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">But they will not get far. The Uruk-hai are too many.</font>

1777
03:13:53,490 --> 03:13:55,870
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">叫女人小孩进入通道上山
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Send word for the women and children to make for the mountain pass.</font>

1778
03:13:56,080 --> 03:13:58,920
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">- 堵住入口!     - 死了这么多人
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">- And barricade the entrance!     - So much death.</font>

1779
03:14:01,130 --> 03:14:04,550
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">人类该怎么对抗这种仇恨?
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">What can Men do against such reckless hate?</font>

1780
03:14:09,220 --> 03:14:10,640
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">跟我一起冲出去
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Ride out with me.</font>

1781
03:14:14,770 --> 03:14:16,390
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">冲出去迎敌
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Ride out and meet them.</font>

1782
03:14:17,140 --> 03:14:19,310
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">为了光荣的牺牲
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">For death and glory.</font>

1783
03:14:19,480 --> 03:14:20,900
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">为了洛汗
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">For Rohan.</font>

1784
03:14:22,400 --> 03:14:23,860
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">为了你的人民
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">For your people.</font>

1785
03:14:24,610 --> 03:14:26,530
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">太阳出来了
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The sun is rising.</font>

1786
03:14:31,030 --> 03:14:34,030
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">五天后等待我的出现
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Look to my coming at first light on the fifth day.</font>

1787
03:14:34,200 --> 03:14:35,580
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">黎明时
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">At dawn...</font>

1788
03:14:35,790 --> 03:14:37,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">向东方看
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...look to the east.</font>

1789
03:14:41,630 --> 03:14:43,250
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">好
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

1790
03:14:45,750 --> 03:14:47,420
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">好
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

1791
03:14:48,760 --> 03:14:51,140
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">圣盔锤手的号角
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">The horn of Helm Hammerhand...</font>

1792
03:14:51,300 --> 03:14:54,100
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">将会响起
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...shall sound in the Deep...</font>

1793
03:14:54,560 --> 03:14:56,560
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">最后一次
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...one last time.</font>

1794
03:14:56,720 --> 03:14:58,230
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">好耶!
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Yes!</font>

1795
03:15:01,270 --> 03:15:05,070
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">这是我们一起拔剑抗敌的时刻
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Let this be the hour when we draw swords together.</font>

1796
03:15:12,870 --> 03:15:14,200
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">邪恶兵团 领死吧
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Fell deeds, awake.</font>

1797
03:15:15,410 --> 03:15:16,450
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">我要以满腔热血
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Now for wrath...</font>

1798
03:15:16,660 --> 03:15:20,080
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">和无比勇气  迎接浴血黎明
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">...now for ruin and a red dawn.</font>

1799
03:15:27,130 --> 03:15:29,380
<font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="76">骠骑勇士 冲啊
</font><font face="华文中宋" size="50" color="#ffff00">Forth Eorlingas!</font>

1800
